Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm your dream girl...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say it just one more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.68,0:00:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You resemble...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...resemble the girl\NI can't stop thinking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,MOM'S SECRET!\NA FEMALE THIEF'S VENGEANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You resemble the girl\NI can't stop thinking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl Asuka Jr. likes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He likes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Meimi! Class is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You were like that\Nthroughout the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the Sister was angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...and gave only you homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.49,0:00:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...Asuka Jr.'s words...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...keep repeating in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got an idea! Asuka Jr.!\NWhy don't you help her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can finish it\Nin 15 minutes, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.56,0:01:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worthless\Nunless you do it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, no.\N- They're going to start up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right, Ryoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.27,0:01:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- What..?\N- The fight didn't start...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You resemble the girl\NI can't stop thinking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.49,0:01:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the crown of the sun,\Nthe Prominence Crown, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.64,0:01:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's showing\Nat the F Art Museum, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think\NSt. Tail is going to target it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.66,0:01:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a treasure\Nlying at the end of the rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prominence Crown\Nwas owned...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...by the Astoria Royal Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the words\Nfrom the Royal Family's crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,On this crown...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...there are seven jewels...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...which, people said,\Nwere from the end of a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Garnet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Topaz...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Emerald and sapphire...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They are seven colored jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the ruby,\Nwhich was in the center,...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...has been missing for some time.\NIt's a famous story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Some say it was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one knows\Nexactly what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,However...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The ruby has resurfaced\Nafter over a ten-year absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard it will go on auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How would it be possible\Nfor St. Tail to pass it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got the front-page article!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You did good research.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I should go to see it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately St. Tail has\Nno intention of stealing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being\Na good friend to Meimi, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. The feeling is mutual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I came here to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NIs something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day, all three of us\Nwent to the F Art Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But since we saw\Nthe Prominence Crown...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...Eimi, my wife,\Nhas been a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do to cheer her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's pray!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure God will help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As I suspected, since that day\NMom has been depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, are depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father said so\Nand is worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:03:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough about me.\NI'll ask Mom to her face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the reason\Nyou're depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...have anything to do\Nwith the Prominence Crown?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You've noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's about time\Nfor me to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I was once\Na mysterious thief, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in a town very far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was called\N"Mysterious Thief Lucifer."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It meant a devil\Nthat had fallen from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a mean thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I stole things from innocent\Npeople time after time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...and became\Nthe talk of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say you wanted me\Nto walk in your footsteps?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing I want you to take\Nis my athletic ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't do bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Originally I started to do it\Nto test my athletic ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But later I discovered\Nthat I couldn't stop being a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For what reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have someone who\Npursued you with all of his heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- Oh, nothing! Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My rival showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I still get irritated\Nwhen I think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A despicable mysterious\Nfemale thief showed up in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She enjoyed\Ndoing things for spite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She targeted whatever item\NI was planning to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She was like a snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mom.\NYou're so competitive...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But one night...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...while I was trying to get away\Nfrom the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...I hurt my ankle because of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in a desperate situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then someone hid me\Nwithout any questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Dad, wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He was living in a small\Napartment and training...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...to be a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have it.\NWhat should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm poor and I don't\Nhave any medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't make so much noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If they fiind me, you'll regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's good for hiding, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever we met,\Nhe gave me an armful of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Only flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only magic\Nhe could do at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...because he always did\Nall that he could do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...and he tried to make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When I watched him like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...I started to think...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the stupid things\NI had been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And I stopped being a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I planned on returning\Nall of the things I had stolen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...to their rightful owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I was planning to do so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...the one thing I couldn't return\Nwas the Prominence Crown's ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way to return it,\Nthat other woman took it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how it ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw the crown...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...I remembered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.78,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to tell Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad knows everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As always\Nhe doesn't mention it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Seira. I'm going\Nto get the Crown's ruby back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The auction place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...the same place as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...I don't think\Nyou should go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm sure Asuka has...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...all of the information\Nabout the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found the warehouse...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...where they're keeping\Nthe ruby until the auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tomorrow night,\NI'm going to the R Warehouse...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...to take the 'Star Ruby.'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, she's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr. is\Nin love with someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't gone home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! I've just opened\Na fortune telling shop near this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come by\Nwith your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How cute! You're blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there! I've just opened\Na fortune telling shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come!\NI'll be expecting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's better\Nif you're not seen with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can peek\Nonly if you can't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice... practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave it to me!\NIt's for my dad and mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the Star Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the day I'll catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the security?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner of the jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...refused the security\Nin the warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but you're the last\Nperson I want to catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,At last I've found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We've put the Star Ruby\Non auction to draw you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mysterious Thief Lucifer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We've discovered\Nthe clue to finding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the last person\NI want to catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why I want to catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I just wanted to catch her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When you showed up,\NI was excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...I didn't want\Nanyone else to have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,From that moment on...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a treasure lying\Nat the end of the rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember\Nwhich royal family it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...but the end of the rainbow\Ncan't exist physically...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shoot! I'll be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of the rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...is a treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he spent\Nthe whole night in the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?\NIt's pretty early...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on duty this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a high fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!\NI'll call your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...that you're here with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I AM RETURNING THIS.\N-ST. TAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...that my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:18:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...can reach you...
